@startuml
!theme plain
title 09. Observability and Rollout Gates
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName DejaVu Sans
left to right direction

rectangle "Benchmark harness" as N1 #D6EAF8
rectangle "Metrics pipeline" as N2 #D5F5E3
rectangle "Failure drills" as N3 #FCF3CF
rectangle "Gate evaluator" as N4 #E8DAEF
rectangle "Release decision" as N5 #FADBD8

N1 --> N2 : TTFT/TPOT tests
N2 --> N3 : telemetry
N3 --> N4 : fault evidence
N4 --> N5 : pass/fail

note bottom
Actor-facing contract: lower-layer resource identifiers remain hidden unless the ADR explicitly defines them as operator-only evidence.
end note
@enduml
